│                                                                              │
│ ### 5. Crystallization output vs. source snapshots                           │
│                                                                              │
│ Crystallization outputs identify concepts such as wallet, brain, intent,     │
│ BSV, identity, certificate, Merkle, runtime, and API [2][4].                 │
│ Some are corroborated by source; others remain conceptual or                 │
│ generated-summary-derived [2][4].                                            │
│                                                                              │
