│                                                                              │
│ ## Bottom line                                                               │
│                                                                              │
│ Semantos-core is best described as an **evidence-grounded semantic           │
│ runtime/app/research platform**. Its strongest confirmed spine is:           │
│                                                                              │
│ ```text                                                                      │
│ Flutter/app + cartridge surfaces                                             │
│ → runtime shell / SemanticFS                                                 │
│ → protocol-types semantic search                                             │
│ → extraction/evidence pipeline                                               │
│ → semantic objects                                                           │
│ → SIR / IR representation packages                                           │
│ → proof/compliance and crystallization tooling                               │
│ ```                                                                          │
│                                                                              │
│ But the repo also contains **legacy, experimental, generated, and partially  │
│ wired architecture**. The final artifact should therefore remain a           │
│ **confidence-labeled subsystem map**, not a flattened “everything is active” │
│ architecture pitch [1][3][4].                                                │
